#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.str.contains.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.str.contains"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:1
msgid ""
"Test if pattern or regex is contained within a string of a Series or "
"Index."
msgstr "测试模式或正则表达式是否包含在 Series 或 Index 的字符串中。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:3
msgid ""
"Return boolean Series or Index based on whether a given pattern or regex "
"is contained within a string of a Series or Index."
msgstr ""
"根据给定的模式或正则表达式是否包含在 Series 或 Index 的字符串中返回布尔值"
" Series 或 Index。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:6
msgid "Character sequence or regular expression."
msgstr "字符序列或正则表达式。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:8
msgid "If True, case sensitive."
msgstr "如果为 True，则区分大小写。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:10
msgid "Flags to pass through to the re module, e.g. re.IGNORECASE."
msgstr "传递给 re 模块的标志，例如 re.IGNORECASE。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:12
msgid ""
"Fill value for missing values. The default depends on dtype of the array."
" For object-dtype, ``numpy.nan`` is used. For the nullable "
"``StringDtype``, ``pandas.NA`` is used. For the ``\"str\"`` dtype, "
"``False`` is used."
msgstr ""
"缺失值的填充值。默认值取决于数组的数据类型。对于 object-dtype，使用 ``"
"numpy.nan``。对于可为空的 ``StringDtype``，使用 ``pandas.NA``。对于 ``\""
"str\"`` 数据类型，使用 ``False``。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:17
msgid ""
"If True, assumes the pat is a regular expression.  If False, treats the "
"pat as a literal string."
msgstr ""
"如果为 True，则假定 pat 是正则表达式。如果为 False，则将 pat 视为字面"
"字符串。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:17
msgid "If True, assumes the pat is a regular expression."
msgstr "如果为 True，则假定 pat 是正则表达式。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:19
msgid "If False, treats the pat as a literal string."
msgstr "如果为 False，则将 pat 视为字面字符串。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:22
msgid ""
"A Series or Index of boolean values indicating whether the given pattern "
"is contained within the string of each element of the Series or Index."
msgstr ""
"一个布尔值 Series 或 Index，表示给定模式是否包含在 Series 或 Index 的每个"
"元素的字符串中。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:29
msgid ":py:obj:`match`"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:30
msgid "Analogous, but stricter, relying on re.match instead of re.search."
msgstr "类似的，但更严格，依赖于 re.match 而不是 re.search。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:32
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.str.startswith`"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:33
msgid "Test if the start of each string element matches a pattern."
msgstr "测试每个字符串元素的开头是否与模式匹配。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:35
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.str.endswith`"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:36
msgid "Same as startswith, but tests the end of string."
msgstr "与 startswith 相同，但测试字符串的结尾。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:39
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:40
msgid "Returning a Series of booleans using only a literal pattern."
msgstr "仅使用字面模式返回一个布尔值 Series。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:53
msgid "Returning an Index of booleans using only a literal pattern."
msgstr "仅使用字面模式返回一个布尔值 Index。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:59
msgid "Specifying case sensitivity using `case`."
msgstr "使用 `case` 指定是否区分大小写。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:69
msgid ""
"Specifying `na` to be `False` instead of `NaN` replaces NaN values with "
"`False`. If Series or Index does not contain NaN values the resultant "
"dtype will be `bool`, otherwise, an `object` dtype."
msgstr ""
"指定 `na` 为 `False` 而不是 `NaN`，会将 NaN 值替换为 `False`。如果 Series"
" 或 Index 不包含 NaN 值，则结果数据类型将是 `bool`，否则为 `object` "
"数据类型。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:81
msgid "Returning 'house' or 'dog' when either expression occurs in a string."
msgstr "当字符串中出现任一表达式时返回 'house' 或 'dog'。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:91
msgid "Ignoring case sensitivity using `flags` with regex."
msgstr "使用带有 `flags` 的正则表达式忽略大小写。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:102
msgid "Returning any digit using regular expression."
msgstr "使用正则表达式返回任意数字。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.contains:112
msgid ""
"Ensure `pat` is a not a literal pattern when `regex` is set to True. Note"
" in the following example one might expect only `s2[1]` and `s2[3]` to "
"return `True`. However, '.0' as a regex matches any character followed by"
" a 0."
msgstr ""
"当 `regex` 设置为 True 时，确保 `pat` 不是字面模式。注意在以下示例中，"
"可能有人会期望只有 `s2[1]` 和 `s2[3]` 返回 `True`。然而，'.0' 作为"
"正则表达式会匹配任何后面跟着 0 的字符。"

